# To Read the latest README.md (markdown) as a screenplay in your web browser, it first needs to be rendered as a screenplay:
# Open command prompt in directory of index.htm file e.g. "C:/MyWebServer/index.htm"
# Copy READ.MD to directory (eg C:/MyWebServer/README.MD)
# In the command prompt window, type the following

$ python -m http.server 8356 --bind 127.0.10.1

# Leave the command prompt window open

# In your web browser, navigate to 127.0.10.1:8356

DONE!